  <brief_title>Latent Tuberculosis Infection in Bone Marrow Transplant Recipients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Observational Study of Usefulness of a T Cell-based Assay for Latent Tuberculosis Infection in Hematopoietic Stem Cell Transplant Recipients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
